Class CombinedDataByYear

java.lang.Object
com.example.moviepopularitybackend.model.CombinedDataByYear
public class CombinedDataByYear extends Object
Represents a combined data object for a specific year, containing information about a country, genre, population statistics, and the number of movies released. This class encapsulates data relevant to both population and movie statistics for a given year and genre in a specific country.
